    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2010/05/you-deserve-a-waffle/#comment-16517"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-05-18T23:39:01-04:00">Tuesday, May 18, 2010 at 11:39 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>The &#8220;Waffle of Insane Greatness&#8221;?</p>
<p>Try it with the full cup of the full fat- cultured buttermilk. (So called &#39;low fat&#39; buttermilk is a bit like non-fat butter.)</p>
<p>It&#39;s the chemistry between the buttermilk, the soda and the baking powder that gives you the loft.</p>
<p>The sugar, caramelizing,gets you the color. </p>
<p>Ross Kane  Warm Beach</p>
    </div>

