    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>hi &#8211; for those of you frustrated with the no print option, try this:</p>
<p>1. highlight the text you want to print (um, usually the recipe)<br />2. select file | print<br />3. look at the dialog box &#8211; there is an option to just print your selection rather than the whole posting. click it<br />4. click ok</p>
<p>i prefer this method to pasting into word since it keeps the URL where i got the recipe.</p>
<p>cindy</p>
    </div>

