    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made these yeasted waffles before and had the same difficulty with the batter not quite filling my Belgian waffle maker.  Yesterday I accidentally added all the ingredients, including eggs and soda.  (Too much kitchen multi-tasking.)  Since I put up the batter at 8am for the next day I covered the bowl snugly and let it proof over night in the fridge.  Turned out to be a superior batch that filled my waffle maker for perfectly full waffles.</p>
    </div>

